              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23537096/" class="">第181页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yisifaerhan/" class=" " title="田彼南山上">田彼南山上</a>
                (.)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="23537096">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">两卷内容多怪力乱神奇闻异事。有重口味记载。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-12-30 23:29</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                两卷内容多怪力乱神奇闻异事。有重口味记载。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







